title: League 2 clubs hit the Hampden trail (Scottish Professional Football League)
text: ( Source : Scottish Professional Football League ) All 10 Ladbrokes League 2 clubs are involved in the second round of the Scottish Cup this weekend, with a place in round 3 on November 28 at stake. There are two all-League 2 ties among the 16
